info.title: XigniteIPOs
info.description: This web service provides IPO data.

GetIPOCalendarOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetIPOCalendarResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetIPOCalendarResult>
    <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
    <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
    <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
    <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
    <tns:IPODescriptions>
     <tns:IPODescription><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
      <tns:IPOIdentifier>string</tns:IPOIdentifier>
      <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
      <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
      <tns:Market>string</tns:Market>
      <tns:MarketIdentificationCode>string</tns:MarketIdentificationCode>
      <tns:Status>string</tns:Status>
      <tns:FilingDate>string</tns:FilingDate>
      <tns:TradeDate>string</tns:TradeDate>
      <tns:EstimatedOfferDate>string</tns:EstimatedOfferDate>
      <tns:OfferDate>string</tns:OfferDate>
      <tns:OfferLowPrice>3.14</tns:OfferLowPrice>
      <tns:OfferHighPrice>3.14</tns:OfferHighPrice>
      <tns:OfferSize>3</tns:OfferSize>
      <tns:OfferPrice>3.14</tns:OfferPrice>
      <tns:OfferAmount>3</tns:OfferAmount>
      <tns:Currency>string</tns:Currency>
      <tns:SmallMarketCap>true</tns:SmallMarketCap>
      <tns:SpecialPurposeAcquisitionCompany>true</tns:SpecialPurposeAcquisitionCompany>
     </tns:IPODescription>
    </tns:IPODescriptions>
   </tns:GetIPOCalendarResult>
  </tns:GetIPOCalendarResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
